# Host-specific NixOS configurations live here, one directory per machine.
# Each host directory contains at minimum:
#   configuration.nix          — the machine's NixOS config
#   hardware-configuration.nix — generated by nixos-generate-config on install
#
# Example layout for a desktop machine:
#   hosts/
#   └── my-desktop/
#       ├── configuration.nix
#       └── hardware-configuration.nix
#
# Add a corresponding entry in flake.nix under nixosConfigurations.
